title: The Order of Dragons T00 -T03 (2008) cbr
description:
FOR CENTURIES, TWO MYSTERIOUS ORDERS HAVE BEEN FIGHTING A MERCILESS WAR...
In 1930, near Ladakh, an expedition is defying the biting cold of the Himalayas. Their trip takes them to the heart of a place no-one has ever dreamed of, where Biblical angels are mixed with Celtic sculptures. Three years later in Berlin, Eva is the helpless witness to the murder of her friend, Elie Strauss, a renowned ethnologist. Behind the scenes, two secret societies who have been warring for centuries are pulling the strings... The investigation begins! 

enjoy
